 3. Query: Find Available ICU Beds (Nearby Hospitals)
db.Beds.aggregate([
  {
    $lookup: {
      from: "Departments",
      localField: "department_id",
      foreignField: "_id",
      as: "dept"
    }
  },
  { $unwind: "$dept" },
  {
    $match: {
      "dept.name": "ICU",
      is_available: true
    }
  }
]);

 Explain:

Filters only ICU beds
Shows available beds across hospitals
Can be extended with location-based filtering
 4. Update: Allocate Bed to Patient
 Step 1: Update Bed Availability
db.Beds.updateOne(
  { _id: ObjectId("bed1"), is_available: true },
  { $set: { is_available: false } }
);
 Step 2: Create Admission Record
db.Admissions.insertOne({
  patient_id: ObjectId("patient1"),
  hospital_id: ObjectId("hospital1"),
  bed_id: ObjectId("bed1"),
  admission_date: new Date(),
  discharge_date: null,
  status: "Admitted"
});

👉 Prevents overbooking because we check availability first.

 5. Aggregation Queries
 (A) Bed Occupancy Rate
db.Beds.aggregate([
  {
    $group: {
      _id: "$hospital_id",
      total_beds: { $sum: 1 },
      occupied_beds: {
        $sum: {
          $cond: [{ $eq: ["$is_available", false] }, 1, 0]
        }
      }
    }
  },
  {
    $project: {
      occupancy_rate: {
        $multiply: [
          { $divide: ["$occupied_beds", "$total_beds"] },
          100
        ]
      }
    }
  }
]);
Hospitals with Highest Patient Load
db.Admissions.aggregate([
  {
    $group: {
      _id: "$hospital_id",
      total_patients: { $sum: 1 }
    }
  },
  { $sort: { total_patients: -1 } }
]);
 (C) Detect Shortage of Critical Resources (ICU Beds)
db.Beds.aggregate([
  {
    $lookup: {
      from: "Departments",
      localField: "department_id",
      foreignField: "_id",
      as: "dept"
    }
  },
  { $unwind: "$dept" },
  {
    $match: { "dept.name": "ICU" }
  },
  {
    $group: {
      _id: "$hospital_id",
      available_beds: {
        $sum: {
          $cond: [{ $eq: ["$is_available", true] }, 1, 0]
        }
      }
    }
  },
  {
    $match: {
      available_beds: { $lt: 2 } // shortage threshold
    }
  }
]);